	div
		ul
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='2') <span class="highlight">conceptualizing</span> - a concept of a new mechanic/level/structure is outlined
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='3') <span class="highlight">prototyping</span> - key aspects are implemented
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='4') <span class="highlight">playtesting</span> - the prototype is shown to the public
